<i>verb</i>: 고다 [고ː다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>고다 [고ː다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. boil to pulp; stew</dd><br>
<dd>고기나 뼈의 진한 국물이 우러나도록 푹 삶다.</dd><br>
<dd>To boil meat or bones until thick stock is made from them.</dd><br>
<dd>2. boil down</dd><br>
<dd>졸아서 단단히 엉기도록 끓이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To boil something so that it condenses hard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>